-- Botswana to Charge Single Corporate Tax of 22% From April 1, Matambo Says
-- B y   J e r r y   B u n g u
-- 2011-02-07T14:05:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-07/botswana-to-charge-single-corporate-tax-of-22-from-april-1-matambo-says.html
Botswana will impose a single
corporate tax rate of 22 percent from the fiscal year beginning
April 1, Finance Minister Kenneth Matambo said in a budget
speech today in Gaborone, the capital.  The tax replaces the two-tier rate of 15 percent corporate
tax and a 10 percent additional tax.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jerry Bungu in Gaborone at 
 jbungu@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
